SING, YE AROADIANS Ι

ΝΕΑΝΒΕΒ, from his cimel, Whom erst the jealous Muses did compel In groves of Arcady to dwell‚

Sends greeting unto every one, And bids you scale the heighte of Helicon, And play Maeonian stringe upon.
